lines.text: Climb up on my knees, kiddies, and I'll tell you a story.
What's this? Stray dogs will be exterminated by 3 o' clock today! That means I've only got till 3, unless I can find a master.
Hot dog! He gave me food.
He looks about as happy as a camel that's seasick. I'm getting out of this neighborhood.
Make way for Harvey and I. Hello, who're you?Happy days!
